- **Hook (0-3s):** "조선 왕실에서 합궁하는 날, 문 밖에서 8명이 지켜봤다?" (Showing a dramatic AI palace scene).
- **Content:** Briefly explain the duty of the 8 court ladies (상궁) during the royal consummation. Use high-density historical trivia.
- **Algorithm Fit:** Pattern Break (Breaking the myth of royal privacy), #역사비밀 tag, emotional/curiosity hook.
