## Findings
- **YouTube Analysis (@honeyjarfinds):**
    - **Latest Level:** High-quality AI-generated visuals (historical, botanical, objects). Dramatic historical mysteries or surprising trivia (Avocado etymology, Joseon palace secrets).
    - **Visuals:** AI illustrations with bold dual-language subtitles (KR/EN). High-contrast thumbnails with yellow/white hooks.
    - **Narration/Pacing:** Fast-paced, clear AI narration, background music that builds tension. 
    - **Hook Strategy:** "Shocking facts" or "The secret you didn't know."

- **Algorithm Analysis (Gemini):**
    - **3-Second Hook:** Start by shattering common sense (Pattern Break).
    - **Dopamine Opening:** Show the climax in the first 0.5 seconds.
    - **Channel Meta:** Use natural sentences in description. Title should have 1 catchy tag.
    - **Keywords:** #미스테리, #놀라운사실, #신박한아이템, #지식쇼츠, #품절대란.
    - **Engagement:** Encourage comments by creating a "playground" or debate in the comments section.
